00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Let's see how to prepare Chicken Gravy

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:06.000
Ingredients are....

00:00:06.894 --> 00:00:08.894
Chicken 1/2 Kg

00:00:10.554 --> 00:00:12.554
Mustard seed 1 Tbl Sp

00:00:13.253 --> 00:00:15.253
Curry Leaves

00:00:15.700 --> 00:00:18.793
Cinnamon, Clove, Fennel Seed 1/2 Tbl Sp

00:00:19.715 --> 00:00:21.715
Ginger Garlic Paste

00:00:23.353 --> 00:00:25.353
Coriander Seeds

00:00:26.274 --> 00:00:28.274
Red Chilli 10 Nos

00:00:29.694 --> 00:00:31.694
1 Chopped Tomato

00:00:31.714 --> 00:00:33.714
Small Onions 20 Nos

00:00:34.134 --> 00:00:36.134
Grated Coconut

00:00:39.774 --> 00:00:41.774
Heat the Pan with 2 Tbl sp Oil

00:00:44.033 --> 00:00:46.033
add mustard seed

00:00:46.194 --> 00:00:48.194
Curry leaves....

00:00:48.194 --> 00:00:48.775
Ginger Garlic Paste....

00:00:50.942 --> 00:00:52.942
Fry until raw smell goes...

00:00:55.100 --> 00:01:01.280
Now add Chicken...

00:01:02.300 --> 00:01:05.140
Add salt to taste...

00:01:07.080 --> 00:01:09.460
add 1/2 tbl sp turmeric powder..

00:01:09.960 --> 00:01:12.540
and fry it again...

00:01:13.600 --> 00:01:16.420
Now close it with lid and cook for 2 min

00:01:17.880 --> 00:01:19.940
Now let's see how to prepare Masala

00:01:20.280 --> 00:01:22.140
Heat the pan without oil...

00:01:22.520 --> 00:01:26.100
and add Coriander seeds and fry it

00:01:27.340 --> 00:01:31.060
Now fry red chillies

00:01:32.580 --> 00:01:38.160
Now add 1 tsp of oil and fry small onions...

00:01:39.660 --> 00:01:44.620
now fry the tomatoes 

00:01:46.420 --> 00:01:49.620
Mix all the fried ingredients in a jar... 

00:01:49.840 --> 00:01:53.260
and make it a fine paste...

00:01:54.360 --> 00:02:00.400
Now add the Masala paste to the chicken...

00:02:00.860 --> 00:02:05.140
add required water...

00:02:05.920 --> 00:02:11.160
Now add coconut, cloves, cinnamon, fenel seeds

00:02:11.160 --> 00:02:14.900
and make a fine paste...

00:02:16.320 --> 00:02:22.420
Now add the coconut paste to the gravy..

00:02:22.940 --> 00:02:26.660
and stir it well

00:02:27.680 --> 00:02:30.780
Add salt if needed

00:02:32.880 --> 00:02:36.660
close it with lid for 5 more mins..

00:02:36.660 --> 00:02:39.880
Now tasty Chicken Gravy is ready

